        {
            "title": "澤連斯基稱烏克蘭的生存取決於盟友提供新的資金",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskiy during a Bloomberg Television interview in Kyiv on Nov. 12.\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/IY..jCI7qlJjW82wswIM7A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/763721f3e654f67375f7e7381217dffc\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskiy during a Bloomberg Television interview in Kyiv on Nov. 12.</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:烏克蘭;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/烏克蘭\">烏克蘭</a>總統澤連斯基懇請歐盟盟友，希望克服在使用俄羅斯被凍結資產問題上的分歧，並表示新的資金對其飽受戰爭摧殘的經濟繼續抗擊莫斯科至關重要。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我希望上帝保佑，我們能得到這個決定，」澤連斯基周三晚間在基輔接受彭博電視台採訪時表示。否則，「我們將不得不尋找其他方案，這關係到烏克蘭的生存。我們非常需要這筆資金。我仰賴這些合作夥伴。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">關於是否動用俄羅斯國家資產向烏克蘭提供1400億歐元（約1620億美元）的貸款，歐盟推遲到12月再做決定，而烏克蘭需要在明年初獲得新的資金。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-21274c25-9419-34f8-a52c-4d899d46eb77-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時，俄羅斯在緩慢推進戰場，並在攻擊烏克蘭的能源基礎設施，在冬季臨近之際削弱對方經濟。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"烏克蘭總統澤連斯基11月12日在基輔接受彭博電視台採訪。攝影師：奧爾加·伊瓦先科/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/wSGVzoqntHxXgVaPpYTtpQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/85a1e86b06c2048db6c7c533985a864d\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">烏克蘭總統澤連斯基11月12日在基輔接受彭博電視台採訪。攝影師：奧爾加·伊瓦先科/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Zelenskiy Says Ukraine’s Survival Rests on New Funds From Allies</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Olesia Safronova、Volodymyr Verbianyi、Anthony Halpin.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BE%A4%E9%80%A3%E6%96%AF%E5%9F%BA%E7%A8%B1%E7%83%8F%E5%85%8B%E8%98%AD%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E5%AD%98%E5%8F%96%E6%B1%BA%E6%96%BC%E7%9B%9F%E5%8F%8B%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E8%B3%87%E9%87%91-082016730.html",
